{"tid":1361104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今次單嘢證明，搵黑社會搞班示威者係好撚低莊ge事","createTime":"2019-07-24T13:50:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T14:41:32.000Z","uid":153600,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0f52851cdf6c71dd63b311f0e05c9142cf8573f5","tid":1361104,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:50:08.000Z","msg":"市民未必支持反送中<br />\n但係黑社會周街打人，打大肚婆<br />\n呢啲嘢係冇一個人容忍到嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次政府呢步棋行得非常之錯<br />\n佢哋嘅末日不遠矣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e89475324a71a4b4cef879b10d1894d9d5e83e2","tid":1361104,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:00:50.000Z","msg":"政府正垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62691f5e5b90397f12f6232c786240768c2f9da1","tid":1361104,"uid":196077,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OrFBUwv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOrFBUwv.png&h=151cff37&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88afbc00e44b4a83b412c4fd6c54ddef3bc309db","tid":1361104,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:22:17.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"804547e12ec61f0660aacbdfb289ffc05801b093","tid":1361104,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62691f5e5b90397f12f6232c786240768c2f9da1","tid":1361104,"uid":196077,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OrFBUwv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%